data.description: This a beautiful example of an executive home. One of the nicest communities in Eustis. Grand entrance, well-manicured community takes you to your lush landscaped cul-de-sac home. Amazing lot size, wide driveway, and breathtaking views of the golf course. The home sits on the 16th hole of Blac Bear Golf Club designed by P. B. Dye. Now step into your grand entrance with beautiful oversize slate flooring throughout the living area. The main living area has the perfect flow for entertaining with an upgraded kitchen open to the family room. Exterior paint was done in 2020, the Water heater in 2020, Roof in 2019, and the Septic cleanout in 2019. HOA includes fiber optic cable and internet. Golf cart-friendly community. Pictures, videos, and description simply does not do this home justice. This home is a must-see.
